1. Username & password
Ask for username and store in a variable
Ask for password and store in a variable
If username is "violet" AND password is "password":
    Say "Welcome to the site, username"
Else:
    Say "Incorrect User and/or password"

2. Firstname or Lastname
Ask for first name and store in a variable
Ask for last name and store in a variable
If first name is "violet" OR last name is "mclean":
    Say "Welcome to the site, firstname lastname"
Else:
    Say "Incorrect User details"